4 CONTAINER RECYCLING REFUND ADVISORY COUNCIL ESTABLISHED UNDER §
5 9–1753 OF THIS SUBTITLE.
6 (D) “BAG DROP PROGRAM” MEANS A PROGRAM THAT ALLOWS A CUSTOMER
7 TO:
8 (1) DROP OFF EMPTY REDEEMABLE BEVERAGE CONTAINERS IN A BAG
9 OR OTHER RECEPTACLE AT ONE OR MORE LOCATIONS FOR A REFUND; AND
