24 (III) AT THE TIME OF SALE, CONTAINS 3 LITERS OR LESS OF A
25 BEVERAGE.
26 (2) “BEVERAGE CONTAINER” DOES NOT INCLUDE:
27 (I) A CARTON;
28 (II) A POUCH; OR

