19 (I) THE WHOLESALE PRICE AND THE RETAIL PRICE OF A FULL
20 REDEEMABLE BEVERAGE CONTAINER SHALL INCLUDE THE REFUND VALUE OF THE
21 REDEEMABLE BEVERAGE CONTAINER; AND
22 (II) A RETAILER SHALL INCLUDE ON A CUSTOMER’S SALES
23 RECEIPT THE REFUND VALUE OF A REDEEMABLE BEVERAGE CONTAINER SOLD BY
