25 (2) THE RETAIL PRICE OF A FULL REDEEMABLE BEVERAGE
26 CONTAINER SOLD BY AN ON–PREMISES SELLER MAY NOT INCLUDE THE REFUND
27 VALUE OF THE REDEEMABLE BEVERAGE CONTAINER.
