28 BEVERAGE CONTAINER BEING REDEEMED IS NOT ACCEPTED BY A REVERSE
29 VENDING MACHINE; AND
30 (2) POST AT THE RETAILER’S ENTRANCE THE ADDRESS OF THE
31 NEAREST REVERSE VENDING MACHINE OR OTHER REDEMPTION METHOD THAT
32 PROVIDES AN IMMEDIATE CASH REFUND FOR REDEEMING EMPTY REDEEMABLE
33 BEVERAGE CONTAINERS.

