15 OF THE SUM OF:
16 (I) ANY INTEREST EARNINGS ON THE DEPOSIT COLLECTION
17 ACCOUNT DURING THE TIME FOR WHICH UNCLAIMED DEPOSITS ARE BEING
18 CALCULATED; AND
19 (II) THE TOTAL AMOUNT OF THE REFUND VALUE RECEIVED FOR
20 THE EMPTY REDEEMABLE BEVERAGE CONTAINERS REDEEMED DURING THE TIME
21 FOR WHICH THE UNCLAIMED DEPOSITS ARE BEING CALCULATED.
